Beverly, Massachusetts.
Pogrebna služba Gallagher, prosim.

00:45:34.400 --> 00:45:37.148
Jutro.
–Živjo.

00:45:42.280 --> 00:45:43.871
Da, živjo,
sem Lee Chandler.

00:45:43.960 --> 00:45:48.157
Moj brat Joseph Chandler
